methods.resetFromArray:
Reset the data and bounds of this chunk to a range or sub-range of the specified array.

:param array: (java.lang.Object) - The array
:param offset: (int) - The offset into array
:param capacity: (int) - The capacity this should have after reset
methods.resetFromChunk:
Reset the data and bounds of this chunk to a range or sub-range of the specified WritableChunkChunk.

:param other: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunkChunk<ResettableWritableChunkChunk.ATTR>) - The other WritableChunkChunk
:param offset: (int) - The offset into other
:param capacity: (int) - The capacity this should have after reset

text:
WritableChunkChunk that may have its backing storage reset to a slice of that belonging to another
 WritableChunkChunk or a native array.
